::KitKat:;

She woke up in the chamber, mostly healed.  She looked and saw the 
holed had healed, but she was still waiting for her strength to 
return to normal.  She closed her eyes and saw Land Mine looking at 
her in her mind.  She whispered,"I'm sorry. It was the only way." She 
sobbed quietly to herself in the CR.
